http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/BEZA-officials-on-study-tour-of-Sri-City/article14009652.ece

An eight-member team, comprising senior officials from the Bangladesh Economic Zones Authority (BEZA), visited Sri City, here on Tuesday. The delegation, headed by BEZA Executive Board Member S.M. Shawkat Ali, were on a study tour to understand the conceptual design and survey the existing infrastructure of the business township.Sri City President (Operations) Satish Kamat and Managing Director Ravindra Sannareddy welcomed the team and gave a detailed presentation on the existing infrastructure.